The paper deals with the security and authenticity of digital documents, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cryptography (cs.CY). The use of QR codes and encryption algorithms also suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), and software engineering (cs.SE).
